ty-give-another-quirky-take-on-marriage/21888196|title=Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Athiya Shetty's quirky take on marriage|publisher= Mid Day|accessdate=11 October 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | ''[[Keep Safe Distance (film)|Keep Safe Distance]]'' || Raama Mehra ||{{hlist|[[Kiran Kumar]]|[[Shahbaz Khan (actor)]]|}}|| Rama Dhanraj Production ||  <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.filmibeat.com/bollywood/movies/keep-safe-distance.html#story|title=Movie Keep Safe Distance, an upcoming thriller by Kiran Kumar and Shahbaz Khan|work=www.filmibeat.com|author=FilmiBeat}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movie/keep-safe-distance/|title=An upcoming movie Keep Safe Distance on Bollywood Hungama releasing on 15 November|work=www.bollywoodhungama.com|author=Bollywood Hungama}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#dbfff8;\" |'''22'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  ''[[Pagalpanti (2019 film)|Pagalpanti]]''|| [[Anees Bazmee]]  || {{hlist|[[Anil Kapoor]]|[[John Abraham]]|[[Ileana D'Cruz]]|[[Arshad Warsi]]|[[Pulkit Samrat]]|[[Kriti Kharbanda]]|[[Urvashi Rautela]]|[[Saurabh Shukla]]}}||[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]], [[Panorama Studios]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zeenews.india.com/bollywood/john-abraham-helps-marjaavaan-in-getting-a-solo-release-2232493.html|title=John Abraham helps 'Marjaavaan' in getting a solo release|publisher=Zee News|date=5 September 2019 |accessdate=7 September 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://mumbaimirror.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/john-abraham-pushes-release-date-of-pagalpanti-to-make-way-for-nikkhil-advanis-marjaavaan/articleshow/71002154.cms|title=John Abraham pushes release date of Pagalpanti to make way for Nikhil Advani's Marjaavaan|publisher=Mumbai Mirror |date=5 September 2019 |accessdate=7 September 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  ''[[Ramprasad Ki Tehrvi]]''|| [[Seema Pahwa]]  || {{hlist|[[Naseeruddin Shah]]|[[Supriya Pathak]]|[[Konkona Sen 