 antagonist... Directed by Gopi Puthran... Produced by Aditya Chopra.|accessdate=1 April 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  ''[[The Body (2019 film)|The Body]]''|| [[Jeethu Joseph]] || {{hlist|[[Emraan Hashmi]]|[[Rishi Kapoor]]|[[Vedhika]]|[[Sobhita Dhulipala]]}}||[[Viacom18 Motion Pictures]] ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1192716947722358785|title=Release date finalized... Emraan Hashmi, Rishi Kapoor, Vedhika and Sobhita Dhulipala... #TheBody to release on 13 Dec 2019... Directed by Jeethu Joseph... Produced by Sunir Kheterpal... Viacom18 Studios presentation.|accessdate=8 November 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#B0E0E6;\" |'''20'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |''[[Dabangg 3]]''||[[Prabhu Deva]]||{{hlist|[[Salman Khan]]|[[Sonakshi Sinha]]|[[Sudeep]]|Saiee Manjrekar| [[Arbaaz Khan]]}}||[[Arbaaz Khan Productions]], [[Salman Khan Films]]||<ref>{{cite web|url= https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1121786019093729280|title= Chulbul Pandey arrives in #Christmas week: 20 Dec 2019... #Dabangg3 release date announcement... Stars Salman Khan... Directed by Prabhu Dheva.|accessdate=26 April 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align:center;background:#B0E0E6;\" |'''27'''\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| ''[[Good Newwz]]'' || Raj Mehta || {{hlist|[[Akshay Kumar]]|[[Kareena Kapoor]]|[[Diljit Dosanjh]]|[[Kiara Advani]]}} ||[[Dharma Productions]], Cape Of Good Films||<ref>{{cite web|url= https://twitter.com/taran_adarsh/status/1122090377651974145|title= New release date for #GoodNews: 27 Dec 2019... Stars Akshay Kumar, Kareena Kapoor Khan, Diljit Dosanjh and Kiara Aalia Advani.|accessdate=27 April 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n{{Portal|Film}}\n* [[List of Bollywood films of 2018]]\n* [[List of Bollywood films of 2020]]\n* [[List of Bollywood films]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{portalbar|Film|Lists}}\n{{2019 films}}\n{{Indianfilmlist}}\n{{Lists of films by langua